A NOON state is a quantum-mechanical many-body entangled state:

  
    
      
        
          |
        
        
          ψ
          
            NOON
          
        
        ⟩
        =
        
          
            
              
                |
              
              N
              
                ⟩
                
                  a
                
              
              
                |
              
              0
              
                ⟩
                
                  b
                
              
